CONTEXT RelationalAdditionTypeCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT RelationalAdditionTypeCheck
{+ Test that relational addition succeeds when concepts can be joined.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts r[A*B]!s[B*C] yielding [A*C]. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[B*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testRelationalAddition: result = r!s

ENDCONTEXT
